dct_title_s: Riparian survey, Beach Haven Terrace, Barnegat Bay
dct_description_sm: This map depicts the Beach Haven Terrace community on Long Beach Island. It shows specific lot information along Delaware and Pacific Avenues and the railroad line along Bay Avenue. Red markings appear to survey a bounded area that details five points.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
The map has a notes inscription that says Riparian Envelope #17.
